. /*
> Paper B best2 standalone empirical tables, 1995-2023 panel.
> 
> Fixed combination:
>     G source = readiness_delta100
>     X source = vulnerability_delta100
> 
> This script produces the retained Paper B empirical outputs: Table 2, Table 3,
> the Full-interaction empirical theta panel, a combined debt-change dynamics
> table, grouped debt-change heterogeneity regressions, and single-crossing
> kink marginal-effect models.
> Tables are written as booktabs/threeparttable LaTeX fragments suitable for
> direct inclusion in a manuscript.
> 
> The dependent variable bond_spreads, selected G source, selected X source, B,
> and all controls are scaled to 0.01 times their source panel values in
> prep_panel before interactions and debt-change variables are constructed.
> */
. 
